## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="46b03-102">单击 "编辑" <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView.ItemEditing>按钮时, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView>控件将引发事件, 但在该项进入<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView>编辑模式之前。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="46b03-102">The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView> control raises the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView.ItemEditing> event when an Edit button is clicked, but before the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView> item enters edit mode.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="46b03-103">("编辑" 按钮是其`CommandName`属性设置为 "编辑" 的按钮。)这使您可以提供一个事件处理方法, 该方法可在每次发生此事件时执行自定义例程, 如取消编辑操作。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="46b03-103">(An Edit button is a button whose `CommandName` property set to "Edit".) This enables you to provide an event-handling method that performs a custom routine whenever this event occurs, such as canceling the edit operation.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="46b03-104"><xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewEditEventArgs>对象传递到事件处理方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="46b03-104">A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewEditEventArgs> object is passed to the event-handling method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="46b03-105">此对象使您能够确定要编辑的项的索引, 并指示应取消编辑操作。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="46b03-105">This object enables you to determine the index of the item that is being edited, and to indicate that the edit operation should be canceled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="46b03-106">若要取消编辑操作, 请将<xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A> <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewEditEventArgs>对象的属性设置为`true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="46b03-106">To cancel the edit operation, set the <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListViewEditEventArgs> object to `true`.</span></span>  
  
